      "@id": "g:stage",
      "@type": "g:Room",
      "rdfs:label": "The Stage",
      "g:description": [
        {
          "@value": "A small theatre stage seen from the wings. Velvet curtains hang heavy on either side. A single spotlight cuts through dust motes, landing on an empty stool at center stage.",
          "@language": "en"
        },
        {
          "@value": "Бархатные шторы обрамляют маленькую сцену. В воздухе пахнет пылью и канифолью. Где-то за кулисами работает магнитофон.",
          "@language": "ru"
        }
      ],
      "rdfs:comment": "art — songs, poems, stories, game rules, audio, video"
    },
    {
      "@id": "g:study",
      "@type": "g:Room",
      "g:default": true,
      "rdfs:label": "The Study",
      "g:description": [
        {
          "@value": "Warm light falls across a desk covered in papers. Bookshelves line the walls.",
          "@language": "en"
        },
        {
          "@value": "Тёплый свет падает на стол, заваленный бумагами. Вдоль стен — книжные полки.",
          "@language": "ru"
        }
      ],
      "rdfs:comment": "articles, dev blog, qualified self, aipassana, documentation"
    },
    {
      "@id": "g:map-room",
      "@type": "g:Room",
      "rdfs:label": "The Map Room",
      "g:description": [
        {
          "@value": "A dim room lit by a single brass lamp. A large table dominates the center, covered by a hand-drawn map with colored pins pressed into it. Rolled charts lean against the walls.",
          "@language": "en"
        },
        {
          "@value": "Тёмная комната с большим столом посередине. Поверхность покрыта рисованной от руки картой, булавки отмечают места, где вы были и куда собираетесь.",
          "@language": "ru"
        }
      ],
      "rdfs:comment": "embedded map of places and events"
    },
